1. Generate a Self-Signed Certificate:
    openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout nginx-selfsigned.key -out nginx-selfsigned.crt
    - Please be reminded to fill common name as your VM's IP. Others can be filled as '.'. Otherwise, it will not work.
2. Copy nginx-selfsigned.key and nginx-selfsigned.crt to ~/nginx
3. Copy nginx-selfsigned.crt to ~/chatbot
4. cd ~/chatbot and then run
    docker build -t chatbot .
5. cd ~/nginx and then run
    docker build -t nginx-project .
6. Edit ~/docker-compose.yaml and fill in your telegram and chatgpt tokens
7. Run docker-compose up -d